## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not cover all possible impacts of SFA due to the rapidly evolving nature of technology and sales strategies. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases based on their publication context. Future research could benefit from empirical studies that measure the direct impact of SFA on sales metrics across different industries.

